Package: gent
Title: Gene-based Association Testing.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Noah", "Lorincz-Comi", , "noahlorinczcomi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0517-2499"))
Description: This package provides functionality to perform gene-based association testing using GWAS summary statistics and a test which has a guaranteed null distribution, separating it from other gene-based association tests. We also introduce a gene-based test which can integrate xQTL information and provide causal inference under the assumptions of Mendelian Randomization and a set of multi-ancestry gene-based association and between-population comparison tests.
